</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   TOKYO (AP) -- Tokyo stocks fell early Wednesday on profit-taking in light
trading. The Nikkei shed 152.25 points, or 0.90 percent, to 16,762.70 in the
first 30 minutes of trading.
</P>
<SUBHEAD>
Pirates 7, Braves 6, 10 Innings
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   PITTSBURGH (AP) -- Wil Cordero led off the bottom of the 10th inning with his
