<HEADLINE> Wall St. Stocks Up in Early Trading  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Stock prices are higher in today's early
trading.
</P>
<P>
   The Dow Jones Industrial Average is up 38 points in the early
going. Advancers on the New York Stock Exchange hold a 7-5 lead
over decliners.
</P>
